summary: An ordinance authorizing the City Treasurer to issue a duplicate Certificate of Purchase for Lot 3, Block 42, Central Seattle Addition which was sold for delinquent city tax for the year 1892, to P. McInnis, and further directing the City Treasurer to pay to P. McInnis the amount now held by him for the purpose of redeeming said lot upon the acceptance of an Indemnity Bond in twice the sum thereof, to be given by P. McInnis.
